    text: [StringData(code: "en", text: "<div class=\"jss788\" style=\"margin-bottom: 32px; font-family: Open-sans, sans-serif;\"><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 MuiTypography-gutterBottom MuiTypography-paragraph MuiTypography-displayInline\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; display: inline;\">he responses were too good not to share. Here are some of our favorites and tips on how to act on them.</p></div><h2 class=\"MuiTypography-root jss787 MuiTypography-h2 MuiTypography-gutterBottom\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 32px; font-size: 3rem; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 60px;\">1. Get a Coach or a Mentor</h2><img src=\"https://images.ctfassets.net/990581qemznk/64CjRV57peGcd34vYYQSnD/04c312c85fc17dd49927bf0dff98289c/hvac-business-development-mentor.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: auto; max-width: 100%; font-family: Open-sans, sans-serif; display: block; margin: 32px 0px;\"><div class=\"jss788\" style=\"margin-bottom: 32px; font-family: Open-sans, sans-serif;\"><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 MuiTypography-gutterBottom MuiTypography-paragraph MuiTypography-displayInline\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; display: inline;\">A business coach or mentor can jumpstart your growth and save you from making costly mistakes that can take years to undo.&nbsp;</p></div><div class=\"jss788\" style=\"margin-bottom: 32px; font-family: Open-sans, sans-serif;\"><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 MuiTypography-gutterBottom MuiTypography-paragraph MuiTypography-displayInline\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; display: inline;\">Where to start:</p></div><ul style=\"padding-left: 16px; font-family: Open-sans, sans-serif;\"><li style=\"font-size: 1.125rem; font-